      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7355-7398",
      "markText": "“进来吧。反正谁都能进来，你自然也能进来。”用生气掩饰喜悦，这对克鲁克斯来说并不容易。",
      "totalCount": 666,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25375893&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7355&rangeEnd=7398",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a923275071833495a92c5a9?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7355&rangeEnd=7398"
    },
    {
