      "totalCount": 595,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25375893&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11943&rangeEnd=12005",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a923275071833495a92c5a9?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11943&rangeEnd=12005"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25375893_4_5953-6041",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5953-6041",
      "markText": "对你来说，什么也不为。可我喜欢这里。我们明天就要去干活。我看到打谷机了，就在往下的路边。这就是说，我们得去背麦包，拼了命地干活。可今天晚上，我就想躺在这里，看看天。我喜欢这个。",
      "totalCount": 585,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25375893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5953&rangeEnd=6041",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a923275071833495a92c5a9?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5953&rangeEnd=6041"
    },
    {
