      "markText": "他把手伸进衣服口袋，掏出卡尔森的鲁格。他拨开保险栓，拿着枪，轻轻按在莱尼背后的地面上。他望着莱尼的后脑勺，望着脊柱与颅骨相连的地方。",
      "totalCount": 576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25375893&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5422&rangeEnd=5488",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a923275071833495a92c5a9?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5422&rangeEnd=5488"
